                                                                                                                    <h5>
                                                                                                                        <a class="expand-link" id="faq-question-ID0EDAAAAAAAAAAAABCA" rel="faq-answer-ID0EDAAAAAAAAAAAABCA"
                                                                                                                            title="Expand/collapse" target="_blank">Can I split my Windows Server 2012 license
