                                                                                                                <div class="faq-answer expand-content" id="faq-answer-ID0EDAAAAAAAAAAAABCA">
                                                                                                                    <p>
                                                                                                                        No. Each license can be assigned only to a single physical server.</p>
                                                                                                                </div>
